  <prompt>
    <goal>Wire the new skill + knowledge base into the discoverability surface so engineers and Claude can find it. Three files updated: (1) root CLAUDE.md Pointers table (§16) — add entry for agent-framework-component skill + knowledge/agent-framework/; (2) .claude/skills/INDEX.md — add the new skill to the index; (3) knowledge/REFRESH-LOG.md — append completion entry for project agent-framework-knowledge-r1.</goal>
    <context>The skill exists physically after task 010 but is undiscoverable unless wired into the indices Claude routes through (`.claude/skills/INDEX.md` is consulted at every session start; root CLAUDE.md Pointers table is the human-facing table-of-contents). This task makes the project visible.</context>
    <constraints>
      - MAIN SESSION ONLY for the .claude/ + root writes (write-boundary rule)
      - Root CLAUDE.md entry MUST follow the existing Pointers table format (Topic | Pointer with link)
      - .claude/skills/INDEX.md entry MUST follow the existing format (skill name + 1-line description + tags)
      - REFRESH-LOG.md entry follows the format established in knowledge/REFRESH-LOG.md
      - Do NOT modify existing entries — append only
    </constraints>
  </prompt>
